        language: "en",
        isAvailable: false,
        publishedAt: "2025-01-02",
        audioUrl: "/podcasts/en/1960s.mp3",
        subtitleUrl: "/podcasts/en/1960s.vtt"
      },
      {
        id: "1970s",
        title: "Melody Mind: The 70s - Disco Fever & Rock Explosion",
        description: "Welcome to the 1970s - the decade of extremes! From the funky disco beats of Donna Summer and Bee Gees that made dance floors shake, to the epic rock operas of Pink Floyd and Led Zeppelin. The 70s brought us Glam Rock with David Bowie, Progressive Rock with Genesis and Yes, and the birth of Punk with the Sex Pistols. A decade that had everything from disco fever to heavy metal - and changed the music world forever.",
