        language: "en",
        isAvailable: false,
        publishedAt: "2025-08-15",
        audioUrl: "/podcasts/en/1970s.mp3",
        subtitleUrl: "/podcasts/en/1970s.vtt"
      },
      {
        id: "1980s",
        title: "Melody Mind: The 80s - Synth-Pop & Hair Metal",
        description: "The 1980s - the golden age of synthesizers and the MTV era! Experience the rise of synth-pop with bands like Depeche Mode, New Order, and The Human League experimenting with electronic sounds. Meanwhile, hair metal bands like Bon Jovi, Guns N' Roses, and Def Leppard dominated the charts. The 80s brought us Madonna, Michael Jackson's Thriller era, and the birth of hip-hop with Run-DMC and Public Enemy. A decade of innovation and excess!",
